reviews.review_text:
Enjoying this one very much Been on an '89 kick lately and happened on this offering this morning. In my opinion, a solid performance. The recording quality is excellent, with the aud mix subtle enough not to overwhelm the SBD but still present, adding a nice layer of energy to the sound.

On a side note, I realize I may be in the minority, but I typically struggle to enjoy Brent's vocals, however he hit the note with Blown Away here, and has grown my appreciation of his contributions during this era, even if it's just a little.

Thanks for the great listen!
